I want to cry but no one wants to hear it. I think this through and through, and time and time again. why does this have to be this way, why is there things I can not change. If I could turn back time, I would. No one can do that and never will and it would fuck up everything as we know it, so it doesn't matter if i could change time. I just don't understand what I do wrong, I fucking hate this so much. I want to lie in my bed and never wake up. I stare at picture upon picture but its not the real thing, It isn't there infront of me. All I can do is read, the one thing I have left to understand what its about. It still doesn't answer  all the questions I have. I hate not knowing this, I hate myself more and more as I stay awake everynight thinking this. I shouldn't get depressed I should be happy but I am alone here in a dark room thinking all the time, everynight with out sleep; it does not help. In the Future, will I be happy? Time will tell.


These words are how I feel about everything that has hapened to me in my entire life.
